data.description: STEP INTO THIS IMMACULATE 3 YEARS NEW HOME. TASTEFULLY TILED ALL THE WAY THROUGH. BEAUTIFUL SOLID SURFACE COUNTER TOPS, UPGRADED FARMHOUSE SINK, DEEP SHELF PANTRY, AND BREAFAST BAR IN THE KITCHEN. BLINDS THROUGHOUT. TREY CEILING LIVING ROOM AND MASTER BEDROOM. SCREEN FRONT AND REAR PORCH LET YOU ENJOY THE AMAZING BREEZE ALL YEAR LONG. WHITE VINYL FENCED BACK YARD. 2 CAR GARAGE WITH ADDITIONAL WINDOW AND EXTRA LARGE UTILITY SINK, WATER SOFTENER AND FINISHED WOOD WALLS. THIS HOME IS LOCATED ON A CUL DE SAC WITH AN EASEMENT NEXT TO IT. YOU CAN PARK YOUR BOAT OR CAMPER ON IT, JUST NOTHING PERMANENT. THIS HOME INCLUDES ALL STAINLESS STEEL KITCHEN APPLIANCES, AND THE WASHER AND DRYER. HOME IS IMMACULATELY MAINTAINED AND EASY TO SHOW WITH SOME NOTICE.
